'''Griff Takel''' was a [[Human/Legends|Human]] [[Gender/Legends|male]] who served as [[Governor/Legends|governor]] of [[Esseles/Legends|Esseles]] to the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] and later the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. He was also the brother of [[Grand Admiral/Legends|Grand Admiral]] [[Miltin Takel]]. In [[1 ABY/Legends|1 ABY]], Takel was involved in a series of [[Terrorist attacks on Esseles|terrorist attacks]] that was considered to be the worst atrocities to hit the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] since the [[Algeran Faction]] attacks.<ref name="GNN9">{{JournalCite|9|Galaxywide NewsNets}}</ref>

